---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppButton from '../components/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Vaitheeswaran Koil Nadi Astrology - Sacred Temple & Center for Authentic Palm Leaf Readings"
  description="Vaitheeswaran Koil is the most sacred center for authentic Nadi Astrology in Tamil Nadu, India. Visit the ancient Lord Shiva temple and experience genuine palm leaf readings by expert astrologers. Get accurate predictions about your past, present, and future from the holy land of Nadi Jothidam."
  keywords="vaitheeswaran koil, vaitheeswarankoil temple, nadi astrology center, sacred nadi temple, lord shiva temple, tamil nadu astrology temple, vaitheeswaran koil nadi, authentic nadi center, vaitheeswaran koil astrology, nadi jothidam temple"
>
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-spiritual to-secondary text-white py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-72 h-72 bg-gold rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-light rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
          <span class="text-gold-light">Vaitheeswaran Koil</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl mb-8 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
          The Sacred Center of Nadi Astrology
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Temple Image Section -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative group animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-accent blur-2xl opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity animate-pulse-slow"></div>
          <img 
            src="/assets/images/nadi/vaitheeswaran-koil-temple.jpg" 
            alt="Vaitheeswaran Koil Temple" 
            class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-spiritual w-full h-auto border-4 border-gold/30 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Sacred Temple of Lord Shiva</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative group animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-spiritual blur-2xl opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
          <img 
            src="/assets/images/nadi/history.jpg" 
            alt="Ancient Palm Leaves" 
            class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-spiritual w-full h-auto border-4 border-gold/30 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Ancient Nadi Palm Leaves</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
          Vaitheeswaran Koil
        </h1>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Vaitheeswaran Koil, a renowned pilgrimage site in Tamil Nadu, India, holds significant importance in Sree Agasthiya Shiva Maha Nadi astrology, a divine form of predictive science. Nestled along the banks of the sacred Vaitheeswaran Temple dedicated to Lord Shiva, this ancient practice is believed to have originated from the sage Agastya, who documented the destinies of individuals on palm leaves thousands of years ago.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">The Sacred Temple</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Vaitheeswaran Koil is a Hindu temple located in the South Indian state of Tamil Nadu. This temple is dedicated to Lord Shiva, who is the third of the Hindu Trinity of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh. As Mahesh, Lord Shiva is supposed to be the destroyer, but in this temple he is worshipped as the God/Master of Healing.
            </p>
            <p>
              The temple's spiritual ambiance and the resonance of the nearby Pamba River add to the mystique of the experience, drawing pilgrims and astrologers alike in search of clarity, healing, and spiritual growth.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Temple Timings</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Morning</h3>
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">06:00 AM - 01:00 PM</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">Evening</h3>
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">04:10 PM - 09:00 PM</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/10 border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Why Vaitheeswaran Koil?</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Most authentic and original Nadi readings available</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Sacred location blessed by Lord Shiva</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Ancient palm leaves preserved for centuries</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Best Nadi astrologers practicing here</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Spiritual healing and guidance available</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-primary text-2xl mr-3">✓</span>
                <span>Online consultations for distant seekers</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center bg-secondary text-white p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Visit or Consult Online</h3>
            <p class="mb-6">Experience the divine wisdom of Vaitheeswaran Koil from anywhere in the world</p>
            <a href="tel:+919500639334" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
              Contact: +91 95006 39334
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppButton />
</Layout>
